transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?

Customer: Ek minute rukiyega, WhatsApp bhi kar deta hu.

Executive: Sir, WhatsApp wala number batana zara?
Customer: 8218
Executive: 8218
Customer: 60

Customer: 3140.
Executive: Sir, maine na aapko WhatsApp kar diya hai sir. Aur sir, maine na apna number bhi save aapko bhej de raha hu. Official aur personal.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Save kar lena sir, theek hai? Abhi se account jo hai na mere paas hi rahega aapka. Account manager ke name se, hai na sir?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Anuj naam hai sir, Anuj Gupta. Ek minute rukiye, main naam bhi aapko bhej deta hu.
Executive: Aapke profile mein bhi mera name dikhayega, abhi dikhata hu main kaise. Aap join kijiyega sir.
Customer: Chalo abhi karta hu join.
Customer: Khul raha hai na.
Executive: Kya sir?
Customer: Khul na raha.
Executive: Are, woh aap number save karenge na sir, tabhi woh link open hoga. Abhi link open nahi ho raha hoga na, blue color ka nahi hoga, black black hoga.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Haan haan, woh number save kar lijiye. Woh jisse maine WhatsApp kiya, woh link open ho jayega.
Customer: Haan.
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Ji sir.
Customer: Haan, sir join kijiyega. Link blue ho gaya?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Ho gaya sir?
Customer: Ye sir kahan ka number maang raha hai ab?
Executive: Kiska?
Customer: Mera hi phone number.
Executive: Nahi, woh Google Meet mein koi number wamber nahi mangega sir. Link pe click karenge, mere pe request aa jayegi.
Customer: Woh sab toh kar raha hu, ho nahi raha.
Customer: You are already in a call likh raha hai.
Executive: Achcha, call mein ek minute rukiyega, ek minute rukiyega. Check kar leta hu.
Executive: Theek hai. Uspe jaise aap link pe click kar rahe hain toh yeh aa raha hai, you are already in call sir, yeh aa raha hai?
Customer: Haan. Pehle woh mangta hai mail ID pe click karne ko bolta hai, uspe click karta hu toh woh likhta hai.
Executive: Haan haan haan haan haan. Pehle jaise link pe click karenge na, toh main email ID bata deta hu aapko. Yeh wala email ID select karna hai aapko. Ramesh R A M E S H K 3168@gmail.com.
Customer: Haan, likh raha hu.
Executive: Koi aur email se toh nahi kar rahe hain sir?
Customer: Nahi, isi se kar raha hu.
Executive: Achcha, phir kyu aa raha hai? Main you are already in a call likh ke aa raha hai bas.
Executive: Ek minute sir, ek minute rukiyega.
Executive: Sir, main na yahan se ek bari jo hai call ko jo main disconnect kar raha hu, phir aap dobara se join kijiye. Uspe click kijiyega jaise abhi aap kar rahe hain, theek hai? Main line pe hi matlab call disconnect kar raha hu, computer pe main line pe hu. Aap aise hi kijiye.
Customer: Haan.
Customer: Theek hai.
